"MAGIC USER" MAGE

   The User of Magic is an intelligent individual, in perpetual striving
to uncover forgotten lore and learn to channel new, more powerful
energies.  The Magic User, or Mage, channels the untapped mystical
energies of the universe through a procedure called 'casting'.

   The mysterious arcane knowledge that these persons wield is         
frightening.  At the outset, these people may not seem to present a    
challenge for a good sword or a stout club, but as their studies grow, 
they have been found to be formidable opponents.                      
The following skills and multi spells are available to magi:

Level    Skill                        Level    Multi Spell
----------------------------          -------------------------------------
1       Fillet                        15      RAY OF DISRUPTION
        Cook                          20      MATERIALIZE
        Scribe                                PRISMATIC SPHERE
22      Spell Recovery                25      ULTRA DAMAGE
30      Shield Block
32      Quick Chant
45      Greater enchant

The following spells are available to magi:
Level    Spell                         Level    Spell
---------------------------------------------------------------------------
1 : Magic missile                      22: Recharge, Gate
2 : Infravision                        23: Haste, Mass sleep
3 : Chill touch                        24: Fire shield
