"TAO"

Tao is the most misterious of all monks. His origin is unknown, but the
rumors say that he is the son of Snow Queen and the White Dragon. Thus he
has the power of Dragons and has the quickness of Snow Queen.
He is very thin, and has long arms and long brown hair. But, don't let his
appereance fool you, cause he is hiding the forces and powers to you
unknown and is able to kill a Black Dragon with single punch!
In Lands of Myst he is also known as the Snow King!

