Classes (professions) available in Land of Myst are the following:

Warrior...............Ancient fighter trusting nothing but his weapon
Mage..................The ruler of mystical energies
Cleric................Powerful priest in service to his deity
Druid.................The protector of Nature elements
Thief.................Always finds a way to get what he wants
Monk..................Master of the unarmed combat
Ranger................Elite forest trooper

See help on them to learn more.
