CLEAR WARM EXTINGUISH

Syntax: clear|warm|extinguish <person>

Use clear to try to clean off the acid of someone's body. Use warm towarm 
up someone who is freezing. Use extinguish to try to put out the flames on 
someone's body.
In either case the success depends upon your dexterity.
