CLERIC

  The Cleric is a holy (or unholy) defender of the tenets of his or her
faith. The arts of healing as well as calling upon the powers of dieties,
these have often been looked at as the saviours of towns and the
diseased.  In these hard times though, some have abused their powers to
inflict harm upon others, summon wild beasts to peaceful villages and
spreading plague and disease over the land.

  Clerics have an ancient belief in not carrying sharp weapons. This class
gives you the wisdom of peace, blessing and healing, though it is possible
to learn and use more violent spells.
The following skills and multi spells are available to cleric:

