#
MULTI

Multi spells are called so because they can not be cast by a single caster. 
In order to successfuly cast the spell caster must be grouped with other 
spell-casters (that means DRUIDS, MAGES or CLERICS). Their total mana must 
exceed the mana needed for casting the spell. Also every single caster must 
be at least MINLV level to participate in casting. MULTI spells are known 
for their undescribable either destructive or defensive powers.

See also: RAY OF DISRUPTION, RESSURECTION, GIVE LIFE, PRISMATIC SPHERE,
          ULTRA DAMAGE, PETRIFY, CREATE RAIN, AREA EARTHQUAKE, RAGNAROK,
          MATERIALIZE
#
MURDER

Kill command to hit another player.  To avoid accidental flagging (i.e.
trying to type "kiss redferne" but accidentally typing "kill redferne")
Note that it is illegal to kill other players.  If you try you will get
a KILLER flag.  If you are flagged as a killer, you are unable to do
damage and other players will be allowed to use the MURDER command to
kill you without being flagged themselves.

See also:  FLAGS
#
NAME

Syntax: name <group_name>

This command will allow you to name your group. You can name your group 
only when you are grouped with at least one other player. Your group will 
then appear in the GWHO list.

See also: GROUP GWHO 
