SKY STARS STARMAP CONSTELLATION

The night sky in the Lands of Myst is host to many stars.
The ancients recognized patterns in these stars and named many
constellations after them.  Throughout the year you may be able
to 'look sky' and pick out some of the most famous ones, including:

&W  Lupus   &G Gigas&M  Pyx &y Enigma&c Centaurus&B Terken&R Raptus
&W   The    &G  The &M  The &y  The  &c   The    &B  The  &R  The  
&WWhite Wolf&G Giant&M Pixie&y Sphinx&c  Centaur &B  Drow &R Raptor&x

Starmap was written by nebseni. Hail to him.
